how <em>loud</em> chanting really is smiled amongst ourselves thought yes expected that So profound was our understanding this place its religion waited for everyone to…do something Roll out their rugs get praying Instead got nothing Not one Turk street even glanced in direction mosque </p><p>Hmmm Ok Well officially secular state an eye towards membership European Union Istanbul fifth largest city world Any urban area size will be less devout than countryside </p><p>Still not so much as twitch Orange juice vendors right yelling random English catchphrases at us Taxi drivers continued 3b.title: Travelblog
3b.excerpt: Why bother with this traveling thing?
3b.content: <p>Whenever Hoss and I make plans to visit a timezone that experiences tomorrow before we do  someone always asks why As in would you want go <em>there</em> spoken the same tone you& 39;d ask guy planning plug his schlong into an electrical socket he hated living so much So Why travel Though know question is generally asked spirit of purest xenophobia it’s still valid </p><p>I don’t have answer </p><p>As previously mentioned doesn’t provide way enlightenment It has certain sexiness among other travelers but friends neighbors coworkers are rarely impressed Travel wont earn promotion nor does it broadcast high definition </p><p>So usually tell people because catching whatever local disease (or falling victim violent splinter group) builds character And what hell gives me chance take pictures something isn’t my dog </p><p>Why not Cabo Siagon instead Bahamas seek discomfort </p><p>Again don& 39;t Serious looking for bigger fix You been Prague Dubrovnik Boy ain’t <em>shit</em> This Swiss bastard over here just got back from Nauru country small by being there human population doubled Next year he’s joining expedition center motherfucking earth there’s obviously measure dick thumping involved I’m immune Once upon time Paris spiked tourist meter; had Eiffel tower cathedral made bones Now Slovenia looks like Austria which Germany insides WalMart If you’ve ever wondered inspire person summit Everest this reason: one up </p><p>Which stupid Who can even remember bastard’s name let alone inform him he& 39;s usurped return these expeditions discontented confused We spend thousands dollars eventually percolates down handful memories maybe good anecdote Spain sangria bridge they threw revolutionaries off Italy shouting sonofabeecha! middle night Cambodia heat hunger butterflies Turkey will be tea learning play backgammon Little things matter </p><p>But start out life muscle sinews leave as collection fills some those spans inside otherwise white noise spent doing nothing no more reliable turn pieces myself </p>

6b.title: Moving
